>\n                <div class=\"container\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-5 offset-md-5 col-6 offset-6\">\n                            <div class=\"wakeup-sec-inner\">\n                                <p>Let each gentle stroke of the Dual-Purpose Line Limiter work towards putting your beautiful expressions to ease, uplifting you, and reminding you of uninterrupted coastlines and laughter-filled air. Smile wide, shine bright and live carefree.</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"true-water-cream\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-true-water-cream.png\" />\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-true-water-cream-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-true-water-cream-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-true-water-cream-mobile.png\" alt=\"true-water-cream\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" /></picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol\">\n                    <picture>\n                        <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/purple-symbol.png?v=1604678960\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/purple-symbol-mobile.png?v=1604678961\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/purple-symbol-mobile.png?v=1604678961\" alt=\"Purple\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid img-responsive\" /></picture>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"purple-symbol-text\">\n                    <p>Symbols in this collection</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"night-slider\">\n                <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-2\">\n                            <div class=\"ovr-hid\">\n                                <div class=\"owl-carousel owl-theme the_velvet-slider\">\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Hibiscus</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider1.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider1-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider1-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider1-mobile.png\" alt=\"Hibiscus\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Hibiscus</h2>\n                                                <p>Plucked one at a time, these tropical beauties hypnotize with their appearance and essence. Packed with beauty benefits, this flower of the Goddess Durga possesses the power to soothe, repair and rejuvenate, arming us with the ability to bloom to perfection.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Kokum</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider2.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider2-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider2-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider2-mobile.png\" alt=\"Kokum\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Kokum</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider2-p\">As the summer breeze gently sways the trees along the Konkan coast, bright purple Kokum fruits fall at our feet. A luscious super fruit, there is as much joy in consuming it for its tart, floral taste as there is in using it for its intense skin regenerative properties.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"mobile-display\">Konkani Script</h2>\n                                                <picture>\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:1351px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider3.png\" />\n                                                    <source media=\"(min-width:768px)\" srcset=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider3-ipad.png\" /> <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider3-mobile.png\" data-src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0456/7610/1786/files/Discover-the-collection-feo-slider3-mobile.png\" alt=\"Konkani Script\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid carouser-image\" /></picture>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-1\">\n                                                <h2 class=\"hidden-xs\">Konkani Script</h2>\n                                                <p class=\"slider3-p\">Just as the Konkan belt delights with hidden surprises, the Konkani / Marathi script is composed of subtle nuances and refreshing accents that set its characters apart. It may be masculine at heart, but it is the femininity in its soul that helps it come full circle.</p>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"item\">\n                                        <div class=\"row\">\n                                            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-12 order-md-12\">\n     